title: Tow strap carrier and dispenser

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a tow strap carrier and dispenser, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a front perspective view of a tow strap carrier and dispenser in accordance with my new design;
FIG. 2 is a front elevational view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a rear perspective view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a rear elevational view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a right side elevational view thereof, the left and right sides of the tow strap carrier and dispenser of FIG. 1 being mirror images of one another;
FIG. 6 is a top plan view thereof; and,
FIG. 7 is a bottom plan view thereof.
FIGS. 1 and 2 include the term “CargoBuckle.” CARGOBUCKLE is a registered trademark, Reg. No. 2,636,949, owned by Indiana Mills & Manufacturing, Inc.
